The main body is a table with seven columns: '#', 'Description', 'EIF', 'attached schedule (Part 2 - EXHIBIT A) Reference #', 'Value', 'Income Type', and 'Income Amount'. A footer section contains a note about an accompanying schedule and a document identifier.
